💕  How do I take care of returns, exchanges or product issue? 💕 
💕 TRACKING SHOWS ARRIVED
There’s not a whole lot we can do when the tracking info shows it as being delivered. Please check with everyone in your household as someone else might have brought it in. Sometimes we have heard of a package going to a neighbor mistakenly or being left at a different/side door. In our experience, usually the package is located.
Most orders are shipped via UPS Mail Innovations or UPS Surepost, and final delivery is by the USPS so we also suggest having the customer contact their local post office and many times they can get in touch with the actual person who delivered it and see if they recall where they left it. It’s best to do that soon after it’s marked as delivered.
💕 NO TRACKING OR NO MOVEMENT
If a package does not show any movement and has passed the allotted time for delivery we will send a new package at our cost to the customer.  We may ask you to check to very the address or supply us with a new shipping address.
SIZING EXCHANGE
We don't offer exchanges or refunds in those situations.
💕 PRODUCT ISSUE
If it is an issue on our end where we sent out the wrong product, wrong size, bad graphic just send us a picture of what you have  received for quality control purposes and we can offer a refund or replacement once the issue is deemed our fault.
US customers have up to 30 days after the shipped date and international customers have up to 60 days after the shipped date.
What we need to make a replacement order:
1.	Please provide the name and email.
2.	Please provide the order number.
3.	Please provide picture of wrong/ damaged item And Shipping Label.
Once we receive this we will print a replacement product and send it right out!

results.title: Rustic Porch Sign Come Sit on Our...  Hokey Pokey Porch Feel Free To Turn Yourself Around Distressed & Antiqued Great Handmade Sign
results.description:
Come sit on our Hokey Pokey Porch! This rustic style sign will add a wonderful touch to your porch... and maybe gain a few laughs!  

*We offer several different items in our shop so be sure to check it out, so you get the one that is the perfect fit for you.

We can also change any wording or leave just the way we have created. Personalized gifts make a great way to go, everyone loves the special touch

* This sign measures approximately 12 x 16 inches and is on 3/8 inch blondewood. 

* Creation is shown in Purple/Ant White,  Blue/Antique White and Brown/Sunflower.  Color Samples can be seen in a variety of sizes at https://www.expressionsnmore.com/color-examples-rustic-laser-engraved/

* Several other color options available in drop down selection. The first color will be the color of the text & second color will be the background.

* Shipment is generally 1 to 3 business days.

* If we are shipping directly as gift, we can enclose a small handwritten note card, be sure to let us know what you want the card to say in the NOTES section when you order.

* For PERSONALIZED signs or signs you want modified please put the information in the NOTES section when placing order.

* Hanger attached on backside for easy hanging

* This is hand painted then laser engraved item is made to order.

We have over 700 items in this Etsy shop so be sure to take a look around in the different sections we offer. https://www.etsy.com/shop/ExpressionsNmore?ref=hdr_shop_menu

Also Be sure to check out our 2nd Etsy shop which includes color creations from the use of our LED UV flatbed https://www.etsy.com/shop/SignsForExpressions?ref=hdr_shop_menu

* PROCESS Our handcrafted creations are made using a 7 step process to create a beautiful expression to be cherished for years to come. Two contrasting colors of paint are applied, the design is laser engraved, a fine hairline is applied to the design which gives an awesome touch. The final touches are completed once it goes through our antiquing process with edges distressed.

* COLOR We have a variety of color choices, but if you don't see what you are looking for, please ask  & we will see if we can make it happen for you. Keep in mind when selecting the color options, the first color is the text color, while the second color is the background. See policies for additional questions/clarification on colors.

* Please note these signs are not massed produced but each is unique and no two are exactly the same.

*When working with wood and the antiquing process, each sign has its own warmth and charm. While we try to get the best wood at the lumber yard, sometimes there will be knots or other slight imperfections in the wood, this is considered adding character to the rustic style of this line of our signs. Thanks for stopping by our shop and please do not hesitate to ask any questions.
